headline.main: Turkey, Greece Seek NATO Mission in Aegean: German Official
headline.print_headline: Turkey, Greece Seek NATO Mission in Aegean: German Official

docs.snippet: Turkey and Greece have agreed to ask for a NATO mission to monitor refugee flows in the Aegean Sea and combat people smugglers, a senior German government official said late on Wednesday....
docs.lead_paragraph: Turkey and Greece have agreed to ask for a NATO mission to monitor refugee flows in the Aegean Sea and combat people smugglers, a senior German government official said late on Wednesday.
